DOC.brief_summary: The aim of the study is to investigate if cow feeding regimes affects concentration of plasma phytanic acid and risk markers of the metabolic syndrome in human.
DOC.brief_title: Effect of Dairy Fat on Plasma Phytanic Acid in Human
DOC.criteria: sign written consent Age: 2042 BMI: 2030 increased risk of developing MS refrain from dietary supplements and blood donations prior to, and during the study poor compliance if they suffering from any chronic or long lasting illness abuse of alcohol or medicine
